## [1.0.0] - 2026-06-14

### Added
- Initial release
- Config flow with dropdown for SE1/SE2/SE3/SE4 price zones
- Support for multiple zones (one config entry per zone)
- Options flow for configurable update interval (15–240 minutes)
- Sensors: current price, next hour, daily avg/min/max, today/tomorrow price lists
- Full hourly (and quarterly from 2025-10-01) price data in sensor attributes
- Swedish and English translations
- example.yaml with Lovelace cards and automation
